misc: Rarely uses his driver, which has raised questions about his masculinity.
biography: Ossi, a competitor known for his strategic approach, hails from the esteemed Kullo Golf Club. A man of meticulous planning and quiet intensity, Ossi's presence on the course is always keenly felt.

Having participated twice in past Hector Trophée tournaments, Ossi is slated to make his third appearance in the upcoming Hector Trophée 2025. While victory has eluded him thus far, his commitment to improvement is evident to all who have the pleasure of watching him perform.

A curious aspect of Ossi's game is his infrequent use of the driver. This has led to some whispered speculation among the golf community. However, Ossi remains unfazed, trusting in his well-honed short game and course management skills to guide him to success.
